Package: radioform
Version: 1.0.0
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libpipewire-0.3-0 (>= 0.3.0), libgtk-4-1 (>= 4.0), libayatana-appindicator3-1 (>= 0.5), libjson-c5 (>= 0.15), libc6 (>= 2.31)
Maintainer: Radioform Developers
Description: System-wide 10-band parametric equalizer for Linux
 Radioform is a free, open-source system equalizer that applies
 a clean, precise 10-band parametric EQ across everything you play.
 .
 It features a PipeWire filter for real-time audio processing and
 a GTK4 system tray app for intuitive EQ control.
Homepage: https://github.com/Torteous44/radioform
